author: Matt Walsh
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh show, an illegal immigrant truck driver was somehow granted a CDL. He then went on to cause an accident that killed three people. This incident was not an aberration. It’s part of a much larger and very disturbing pattern. We’ll discuss. Also, Barack Obama is building a giant hideous monument to himself in Chicago and the local residents aren’t happy about it. And Joy Reid declares that white people have never invented anything. Is that true? Obviously not but we’ll talk about it.
